Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.67,Dragner opchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}和我擦乾眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.30,Dragner opchbig5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7}沒有聖劍也無所謂
